00:14:38.017 --> 00:14:43.620
82 and 1 half to 36 and 1 half.
 

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:44.620
So what should you do?
 

00:14:44.620 --> 00:14:55.590
 
 

00:14:55.590 --> 00:14:56.720
What should you do now?
 

00:14:56.720 --> 00:14:58.948
So I've done some rounding here
