00:15:27.634 --> 00:15:28.779
either direction.
 

00:15:28.779 --> 00:15:34.788
What should you do?
 

00:15:34.788 --> 00:15:37.029
You're not going to bet (33,22)
again.

00:15:37.029 --> 00:15:38.998
You're going to make a
