going to be 64 again,

00:16:10.193 --> 00:16:13.379
and adding this is 64 again,
right?

00:16:13.379 --> 00:16:15.590
So you've locked in whatever
this number is.

00:16:15.590 --> 00:16:18.899
So in the first step you made a
bet to lock this number in.

00:16:18.899 --> 00:16:22.178
In the second step you made a
bet to lock this number in.

00:16:22.178 --> 00:16:26.220
You're always locking in where
you were before.

00:16:26.220 --> 00:16:28.210
So that bet is changing each
time,

00:16:28.210 --> 00:16:30.038
but you're always locking in
what you were before,

00:16:30.038 --> 00:16:34.351
because after the Yankees have
won a game now the next game is

00:16:34.351 --> 00:16:36.120
not quite as important.
 

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:39.958
Time is running out on the
