00:16:44.269 --> 00:16:52.750
So you make a smaller bet up
here than you did before.

00:16:52.750 --> 00:16:55.759
So why is that locking
everything in?

00:16:55.759 --> 00:16:58.515
Because this average is now 64,
what it was here,

00:16:58.515 --> 00:17:02.250
but don't forget you'd already
made the initial bet to lose 22.

00:17:02.250 --> 00:17:06.135
So you've locked in 44 now here
and also 44 here because you

00:17:06.135 --> 00:17:08.640
