00:25:40.769 --> 00:25:42.828
replicate those cash flows.
 

00:25:42.828 --> 00:25:46.119
You can go out into the market
and buy those cash flows,

00:25:46.119 --> 00:25:49.769
the very cash flows you know
the mortgage is going to make.

00:25:49.769 --> 00:25:50.880
How can you do that?
 

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:54.630
Well, because at the first
step--remember what this says.

00:25:54.630 --> 00:25:58.130
The first step the price is 98.
 

00:25:58.130 --> 00:25:59.920
The interest rate could go up
or down.

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:03.980
