00:51:55.965 --> 00:51:58.480
the mortgage,
sorry.

00:51:58.480 --> 00:52:01.579
The value of the non-call,
the value of the call,

00:52:01.579 --> 00:52:05.262
so as the interest rate goes up
you owe less money because

00:52:05.262 --> 00:52:08.039
