00:57:30.789 --> 00:57:32.570
So hold those two things.
 

00:57:32.570 --> 00:57:37.389
I claim that'll pay you 100.6
here and 107.11 here.

00:57:37.389 --> 00:57:40.405
How do I know that without
having to even calculate

00:57:40.405 --> 00:57:41.309
