00:57:41.309 --> 00:57:44.248
Well, the Treasury's going to
pay the same amount here and

00:57:44.248 --> 00:57:44.610
here.
 

00:57:44.610 --> 00:57:45.960
It's going to be a constant.
 

00:57:45.960 --> 00:57:49.985
This thing, since its gap is 38
dollars and I only hold 1 sixth

00:57:49.985 --> 00:57:52.349
of it,
it's going to pay me exactly 6

00:57:52.349 --> 00:57:55.789
and 1 half more down here than
