00:57:55.789 --> 00:57:58.280
instead of 38 will be 1 sixth of
that,

00:57:58.280 --> 00:57:59.730
which will be 6 and 1 half.
 

00:57:59.730 --> 00:58:01.829
So the gap will exactly match
