00:58:01.829 --> 00:58:05.083
So added that to the Treasury's
constant payments I'm going to

00:58:05.083 --> 00:58:08.126
get something over here and 6
and 1 half dollars more than

00:58:08.126 --> 00:58:09.139
that down here.
 

00:58:09.139 --> 00:58:11.190
But since I've paid the same
amount,

00:58:11.190 --> 00:58:15.889
98.8, it's going to have to be
that that constant was exactly

00:58:15.889 --> 00:58:19.179
right to make this be 100.6 and
107.11,

00:58:19.179 --> 00:58:22.201
because both the 1 year
