01:00:21.590 --> 01:00:24.320
It won't change the numbers,
but.

01:00:24.320 --> 01:00:26.650
So it's paying--I didn't write
it down.

01:00:26.650 --> 01:00:28.570
So this thing is not paying 121.
 

01:00:28.570 --> 01:00:29.750
It's also paying the coupon.
 

01:00:29.750 --> 01:00:31.420
This is the present value of
