01:01:46.320 --> 01:01:47.719
Why is that?
 

01:01:47.719 --> 01:01:57.460
Because this number 140.93
divided by 6 is exactly this

01:01:57.460 --> 01:02:06.164
evaluated at this price,
1 half over 1.06 times this,

01:02:06.164 --> 01:02:12.190
this is the price 1 half times
