01:02:12.190 --> 01:02:17.449
All right, so that bond which
cost 140.53 how did I get 140.53

01:02:17.449 --> 01:02:18.139
there?
 

01:02:18.139 --> 01:02:20.880
I took the price of 1 dollar in
